  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Today's math lesson was simple in theory: take a ruler and measure five random objects in the classroom, in inches.",
      "zh": "今天的數學課理論上很簡單：拿一把尺，用英吋量五樣教室裡隨便選的物品。"
    },
